рџЏ—пёЏ Model Architecture

The CNN model includes:

Convolution Layers
MaxPooling Layers
Dropout Layers
Dense Layers
ReLU Activation Function
Sigmoid Activation Function

These layers help the model learn image patterns effectively and improve prediction accuracy.

